Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:23.49,Flashback,Yae,0,0,0,,Acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:28.09,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Yes. You have a Sense that would \Nshine brilliantly onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.08,Flashback,Yae,0,0,0,,Sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:32.18,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Why not come to SIRIUS?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:38.67,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,If you're interested at all,\Ncome check us out.
