Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.85,0:00:48.38,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:55.12,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she speaks, everyone's enraptured, \Ndrawn into the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:58.36,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she looks sad,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:00.25,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,{\i1}we all feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.65,0:01:02.75,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,{\i1}When she smiles...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.57,0:01:08.55,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,{\i1}She was the one who taught me that theater \Nis beloved throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:12.19,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,{\i1}That it brings happiness to so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.56,0:01:15.70,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if I can do that too...
