Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:55.15,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,"I need to get better for Yae{**-chan}'s sake..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.06,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,That's all I could think\Nwhile playing Aladdin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:00.77,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You need to get more familiar with the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:02.03,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:02.99,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:07.79,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,1)\shad0\fnTimes New Roman\fs24\c&H493268&\b1\frz17.87\pos(505.911,566.307)\3c&H8E81B0&}Arabian Nights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:07.78,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'm going to try playing various versions \Nof Aladdin, so make sure you watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:09.70,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Okay!
