Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.55,Default,Reporter,0,0,0,,We'll send you the interview article soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:19.25,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,Great. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.94,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,You have so many press requests, \NI hardly know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.31,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,If possible, I'd like to do them with Kokona{**-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.58,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Now that theater is so mainstream,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:33.75,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,audience-goers are connoisseurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.24,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if you're the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:38.31,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,If an actor has no presence, they vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.54,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,It's because Kokona{**-san} is working so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:44.33,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,that I'm able to play the\NGenie the way I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:47.54,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Is it guilt that's making you \Nworry so much about Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:48.60,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:53.06,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,You had a hunch that this \Nwould happen, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.05,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Not giving your all up on that stage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:59.80,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,isn't just rude to your costars.\NIt's rude to the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:04.02,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:12.99,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,A kind Aladdin, a powerful \NAladdin, an anxious Aladdin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:20.76,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I played various versions, \Nso which one felt right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.20,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,You really are amazing, Shizuka{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.31,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,If only I could act like that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.57,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You'll be the one on stage, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.21,0:04:34.71,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Anyway, I guess you'll just have \Nto try various Aladdins for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.36,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,You mean I'll have \Nto change it up each time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:40.83,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,You'll be working to perfect the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.83,0:04:42.51,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I think that's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:46.27,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,I'm not going to cause trouble \Nfor everyone, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:52.92,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.94,0:04:56.89,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,I don't even know what to say to that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:01.15,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Oh, I found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:05.90,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to rehearse with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:06.64,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:07.90,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:11.00,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Kokona just said something \Nreally interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:14.06,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.54,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,We promise it'll work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.91,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,If you change the way you play the role, \Nwe have to change the direction, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:23.16,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,And wanting to do that\N for every performance is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:26.41,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,The lead changing the role with each show?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:28.40,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I've never heard of anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:32.80,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,It would also mean changing up\N our interactions with her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:37.57,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,The other actors and staff won't\N take kindly to grandstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:41.44,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,Experimental acting during\N a real show is unprofessional.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.75,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you take care of that beforehand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:49.57,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,The production's going pretty well so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.62,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,Just learn from this for next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:52.81,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,Isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.47,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:58.93,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,If I give up now, I don't think I'll \Never be able to take the stage again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:01.58,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Please, let us do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:02.95,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.46,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Talk about selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:10.55,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,My parents are both pretty nice, \Nbut they fight a lot when it comes to acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.97,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Neither one ever backs down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.15,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,They've both told me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:20.45,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,that World Dai Stars should \Nbe just impertinent enough
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:23.35,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,to never relent until\Nthey get what they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:27.14,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,I'm fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:30.94,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,This'll put the most stress on you, Yae.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:33.18,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,And there's no guarantee it'll go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.36,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.86,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,I'll figure things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:39.03,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yae{**-chan}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.82,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,I'm fine with it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:44.58,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Not that I have that many \Nscenes with Aladdin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:47.41,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I have a lot, but I'm cool with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.16,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:55.10,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,The Leila within me said, "Squee."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.79,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Leila doesn't say, "squee"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:07:00.57,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Well, I'm fine with it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:01.80,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Panda{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:06.93,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,It's totally illogical, unprofessional, \Nand a whole mess of trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:10.87,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,But hey, it sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:13.83,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,What do you say, Hiiragi{**-san}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:19.61,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.34,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,But you only get to change up\Nyour performance once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:27.33,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Any more would be too much \Nof a burden for everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:29.88,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,If you need to get the role down,\Ndo it tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.88,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,And if she doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:34.62,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Then she'll continue playing \Nthe role as she has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:39.39,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Even if that means Kokona \Nwill never take the stage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:40.37,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.88,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.23,0:07:53.64,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,We'll hold a meeting tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.64,0:07:57.04,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Then we'll do a light dress rehearsal \Njust prior to showtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:59.88,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Inform the other staffers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.19,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:05.33,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,This won't be easy,\Nbut I'm counting on all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:06.53,Default,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.70,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.70,0:08:09.71,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.23,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:16.67,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Uh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.44,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,We should get back to rehearsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:20.07,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.44,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:26.62,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Did Hiiragi{**-san} just... smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.64,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,It took you too long to find the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.45,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:38.41,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.35,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.33,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:45.97,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,You said that you two were \Npracticing various Aladdins, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:50.55,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Did you mean the versions \Nothers have played before you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.73,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:53.02,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Forget all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:53.73,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:56.72,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,There's no point in imitating other actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:59.35,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Let's start right now by \Ndoing one scene at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.93,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I'll play the other roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.36,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:07.35,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I'll show you exactly how to use your Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.65,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,My Sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.19,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,How to use it?
