Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:36.31,Flashback,Kudo,0,0,0,,Yae, where are you off to in such a rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:39.97,Flashback,Yae,0,0,0,,I'm looking for Hiiragi{**-san}! \NI wanted to rehearse with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:45.04,Flashback,Shamo,0,0,0,,Are you really going to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:45.90,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:50.79,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,After this performance, \NI'll step down from the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:54.60,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,From now on, please let me support \NSIRIUS from behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:57.98,Flashback,Shamo,0,0,0,,But you're still young \Nand have a great Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:02.16,Flashback,Shamo,0,0,0,,You have offers from various \Nother troupes, too, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:06.37,Flashback,Shamo,0,0,0,,If you transfer, I'm sure you'll find \Nyour path to becoming a World Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:10.75,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,It was SIRIUS that shepherded me \Ndown the path to acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:14.87,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Until SIRIUS produces a World Dai Star,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:18.02,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I have no plans to take the stage again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:27.41,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to become a World Dai \NStar as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:34.03,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(964.368,386.907)\org(964.368,386.907)\fscx100\fscy99.662\frx-1.67\fax0\fnArial\fs108\b1\xbord0\ybord0\c&H8A62FD&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(1200,1)}S{\c&HF9AA06&}t{\c&H30C2FF&}e{\c&H8A62FD&}l{\c&HF9AA06&}l{\c&H30C2FF&}a {\c&H8A62FD&}o{\c&HF9AA06&}f{\c&H30C2FF&} t{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e {\c&H30C2FF&}T{\c&H8A62FD&}h{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}a{\c&H8A62FD&}t{\c&HF9AA06&}e{\c&H30C2FF&}r{\c&H8A62FD&}:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.45,0:10:42.03,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,The changed marks, lighting, \Nmusic cues, and direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:44.42,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,You've got it all down now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.29,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Kokona!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:48.29,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:49.70,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:54.54,Default,Kudo,0,0,0,,Well, we'll need to make some minor \Nadjustments, but this should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.67,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Well, Kokona? Have you hit your limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:00.54,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,No... I can keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:03.69,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Okay. Then let's continue \Nrehearsing until you can't anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:05.62,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,to increase the precision of your Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.62,0:11:06.57,Default,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:10.19,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,1)\fnTimes New Roman\b1\i1\blur3\fs36\bord3\shad0\c&H40637B&\3c&H201527&\frz353\pos(731.814,245.199)}Arabian Nights{\c&H406380&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:10.19,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,1)\fnTimes New Roman\b1\fs36\shad0\c&H4A518B&\3c&H17116D&\frz351.1\pos(713.355,436.338)}Sold Out   Thank You
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:10.19,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,That person totally cut in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:12.94,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I made it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.18,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,We get to see Yae{**-chan}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.19,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:26.70,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}The curtain's rising, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:29.39,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah. I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:35.82,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go, Shizuka{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.15,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,The people in this town never look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:48.09,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,They're too busy running their shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:55.61,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,No one ever sees me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:59.20,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,No one even knows my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:04.10,Default,Shizuka (Aladdin),0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:04.10,Overlap,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:06.11,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,I love this city!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.22,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,Everyone's desperate to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.16,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,At night, they all get drunk to the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:13.19,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,You can smell the sweet aroma \Nand hear the laughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.10,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,See? It's starting again tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:21.42,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,Another Arabian night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:27.30,Lyrics,Song,0,0,0,,Make your dreams come true
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:32.11,Lyrics,Song,0,0,0,,Leggo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:35.73,Lyrics,Song,0,0,0,,Sing and dance to your heart's content
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:39.25,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Did her acting skills go up another notch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:39.32,Lyrics,Song,0,0,0,,A mirage rises from the heat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:41.68,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Aladdin's presence on stage is stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:43.11,Lyrics,Song,0,0,0,,All I can rely on is my body
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.79,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:48.00,Lyrics,Song,0,0,0,,My earnest eyes just look ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:45.74,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,It's the Prince from {\i1}The Little Mermaid{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:52.49,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um, when you say how to use my Sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:55.18,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,When you played the Prince \Nfrom {\i1}The Little Mermaid{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:57.76,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,what were you thinking about, Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:00.32,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,I was just so caught up in the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.32,0:13:03.97,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,I figured that was how Shizuka{**-chan} \Nwould play the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:09.96,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,It was a short scene, but you could \Nclearly tell what the Prince was feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:12.75,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,If you're just {\i1}playing{\i0} the role,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:15.40,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,you can't express\Nwhat a character is feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:20.15,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Shizuka must be strangely good \Nat blending into roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:23.97,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Your acting style is close \Nto perfect immersion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:25.40,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,Perfect immersion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:30.82,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,That might be the ideal type of \Nacting you want to adopt, Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:35.04,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:35.92,Default,Sasuga (Princess Leila),0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:39.44,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}What Aladdin feels here\Nis a faint sense of hope
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:42.78,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}after meeting Leila, who's from \Na completely different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:46.82,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just maybe, he can finally escape\Nhis days of fighting for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:48.18,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:49.72,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:56.66,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,I'd like to talk with \Nyou for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:07.71,Default,Panda (Abdullah),0,0,0,,Will you live your whole life being poor,\Nor will you step forward into a new life?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:11.33,Default,Panda (Abdullah),0,0,0,,The choice is entirely yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:14.26,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aladdin knows nothing \Nabout the outside world,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:16.32,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}so everything outside \Nthe city is unknown to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:20.59,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}So to meet a mysterious man\Nwho sees right through him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.82,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's nervous and anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:29.10,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's actually pale and shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:32.90,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like she's truly terrified\Nto go into that cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.79,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through Aladdin, even the \Naudience is feeling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:44.00,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}To Kokona, Shizuka is the ideal actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:48.51,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}All she needs to do now is put in \Na little sweat to reach that ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:52.82,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I've drilled the basics into \NKokona these past three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:56.89,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had her play a variety of roles \Nso she could gain experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:59.69,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,This is the lamp he's after.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.38,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,Finally, my life will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:06.89,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}The comprehension to perfectly \Ndraw out the emotions of a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:10.69,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}The keen expressive ability to convey \Nthose emotions to the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:15.13,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}The two of them together bring \Nthe ideal performance to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:17.88,Default,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:20.16,Default,Kokona and Shizuka,0,0,0,,{\i1}our Sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:31.64,Default,Yae (Genie),0,0,0,,I'm the Genie of the Lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:34.62,Default,Yae (Genie),0,0,0,,I serve whosoever possesses my lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:38.41,Default,Yae (Genie),0,0,0,,I shall grant you any \Nwish your heart desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:42.66,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,You must be the genie from this lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.18,Default,Yae (Genie),0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:48.42,Default,Yae (Genie),0,0,0,,You're in luck! You're one of a \Nselect few who get to see my powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:52.55,Default,Yae (Genie),0,0,0,,Let's start the music!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:57.61,Lyrics,Song,0,0,0,,Gather the moments where the highlights burst
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:02.23,Lyrics,Song,0,0,0,,Surprise into when there was magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:10.41,Lyrics,Song,0,0,0,,(So just special for you)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:13.79,Lyrics,Song,0,0,0,,With everything just how you like it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:18.76,Lyrics,Song,0,0,0,,A place where wishes came true, \Nthat's the world we were in
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:22.15,Lyrics,Song,0,0,0,,(Dream like this come true, \Ndream like that come true)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:26.33,Lyrics,Song,0,0,0,,(Ah) Even when I went into \Nthe Lost Woods alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:24.92,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,The atmosphere just completely changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.34,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,It's like a concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.29,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, I was never scared
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:30.21,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you get swallowed up here,\Nthis will be Niizumacchi's stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:31.07,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Because I've got adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:34.26,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,(When I was little, the world was mysterious)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:35.17,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,(Uh)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.78,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your performance earlier was brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.09,0:16:44.02,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I can't let you outshine me on this stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:50.63,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,Wow! You're totally amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:52.13,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:54.69,Overlap,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,{\an8}Show me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.40,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not fazed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:59.59,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,She's planning to play Aladdin as he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.35,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,My heart just squeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:04.41,Overlap,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,{\an8}You really surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:05.95,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Kokona smiles, everyone smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:10.55,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,{\i1}When Kokona speaks, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.84,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:41.44,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yae{**-chan}'s flaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:42.89,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.74,0:17:46.09,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,No one's realized it yet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:50.14,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Her Sense that allows her to express her \Nemotions to the audience through song
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:52.03,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,is entirely too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:58.71,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,By the end of a show, the audience \Nwill only remember Yae Niizuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.48,Flashback,Shizuka,0,0,0,,But for a performance, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:06.77,Flashback,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,The world will never acknowledge an actor \Nwho destroys a performance as a Dai Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:10.79,Flashback,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um... Why are you telling us this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:16.08,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,Do you hear the revelry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:21.33,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,Everyone's intoxicated \Nby the Arabian night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:28.71,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,Just as you wished, Leila and I \Nare living happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:32.10,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:37.10,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,If I ever get to see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:44.49,Default,Kokona (Aladdin),0,0,0,,No... No more wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:24.31,Default,Audience A,0,0,0,,Yae{**-chan}'s Genie was just like \NI heard. She was super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:29.73,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs42\fay-.16\shad0\c&H5B5B73&\3c&HD7D6F0&\b1\move(2046.462,331.845,1146.462,331.845)}Merchandise Area
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:26.97,Default,Audience B,0,0,0,,Right? I think it was \Neven better than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:29.73,Default,Audience B,0,0,0,,Especially that last scene \Nwith Aladdin and the Genie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:34.48,Default,Audience C (little girl),0,0,0,,Um! I'd like a picture of Aladdin... \NOf Kokona Otori{**-chan}, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.98,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(1026.174,886.557)\org(1025.232,886.557)\fscx98.966\fscy97.573\frz-32.584\fry0\frx5.46\fax-0.032\fnArial\fs30\b1\i1\xbord0\ybord0\c&H262234&\3c&HE7E9E9&}T-shirts 2,500 yen
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.99,Default,Staff,0,0,0,,Here you go. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:41.58,Default,Audience E,0,0,0,,Was her name Kokona Otori? \NI heard she's new, but she's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:51.02,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,I guess I was destroying the performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:54.14,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,To think that I could do \Njust fine all by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:55.88,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,I was being vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.19,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,If you want to become a World Dai Star,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.62,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I don't think you can do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:04.25,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Sadly, I realized that too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.98,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,I'll become one no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.45,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,I'll work together with \NKokona{**-san} and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:15.25,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:17.51,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,One day, will you join me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:19.54,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:23.91,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Hiiragi{**-san}... and Yae{**-chan}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:25.94,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:30.12,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Oh, um... Panda{**-chan} said \Nyou'd probably be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:31.68,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Am I interrupting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:33.43,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:34.53,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,So, what do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:35.80,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:40.41,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me with my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:43.94,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Don't be so off the cuff next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:45.90,Default,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,It's not good for my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:46.67,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:48.57,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,Kokona{**-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:49.55,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:52.14,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:52.79,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:55.80,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,Tonight's performance was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:21:01.06,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to tomorrow's \Nshow as well, Kokona{**-san}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.83,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:09.07,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Whoa, Dugong{**-chan}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:11.97,Default,Koknoa,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:15.84,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,It appears as though Dugong{**-san} \Nenjoyed the performance, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:18.08,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Is that what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:32.18,Default,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Hey! Now the fireworks have started!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:35.38,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Come on! You know that \Nwas too awkward to butt in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:38.15,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,This is what people mean when \Nthey say you need to read the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:39.70,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,You were watching?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:41.97,Default,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Festival time, festival time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:44.14,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,Oh, I love festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.14,0:21:46.32,Default,Panda,0,0,0,,Festival time! Festival time! Festival time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:47.25,Overlap,Kokona,0,0,0,,Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:49.16,Default,Yae,0,0,0,,They're very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:52.28,Default,Kokona,0,0,0,,Up they go!
